Package: provenance
Type: Package
Title: Data visualisation for Provenance Analysis
Version: 0.1-2
Date: Sys.Date()
Author: Martin Rittner
Maintainer: Martin Rittner <sw@thegeologician.net>
Description: Easy visualisation and analysis of sediment provenance proxy data as used in the Earth Sciences. Provides plotting functions for KDEs, MDS and 3-way MDS maps, allowing multi-proxy sample comparisons.
License: GPL (>=2)
Depends: ggplot2, MASS, scales, reshape2
Suggests: gdata, CDFt, vegan
